  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The creature inside wobbles its blob-like body back and forth, yearning to be hatched.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for an <span class=\"name name-technology\">autonomous</span> personality.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个有生命的、可生育的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>寄宿其中的小生物正在前后扭动着团块状的躯体，看上去已经迫不及待想要脱壳而出。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-technology\">自主</span>的基因潜质。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>這隻生物在裡面不斷搖晃著自己黏液般的身軀，期待著孵化出來的日子。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-technology\">自主</span>性情。"
  },
